2ï¸âƒ£ Callout Value (Percentage of "Yes" Orders)

IsOrderOlderThan18M_Percentage =
VAR YesCount = COUNTROWS(FILTER('Snapshot', 'Snapshot'[Is Order Older Than 18 Months] = "Yes"))
VAR TotalOrders = DISTINCTCOUNT('Snapshot'[Doc Nbr])  -- Count of unique orders
VAR Percentage = DIVIDE(YesCount, TotalOrders, 0) -- Avoid division by zero
VAR Icon =
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        Percentage > 0.5, "ðŸ”´",  -- Red if more than 50% of orders
        Percentage > 0.2, "ðŸŸ ",  -- Orange if 20%-50%
        "ðŸŸ¢"                      -- Green if less than 20%
    )
RETURN
    Icon & " " & FORMAT(Percentage, "0.0%")

ðŸ‘‰ Example Output: ðŸŸ¢ 12.5%
